{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"call_F7AljEP0uipBmmXexcGV24jM","type":"tool_result","content":"/home/vasilis/LMTHING/lmthing/sdk/org/scenarios/README.md:14:| [06](./06-tanzania/scenario.md) | **Tanzania trip** — one attachment becomes spaces + a live, updatable app | file ingest (`system-files`); per-leg spaces; live-project app (`writeProjectTable`/`Page`/`Api` + rows seed); `db:write` later-update; compound + multilingual ask |\n/home/vasilis/LMTHING/lmthing/sdk/org/scenarios/harness/lib/local.mjs:11: * tanzania-trip / life-admin / …), so concurrent lanes never collide on the single runtime root.\n/home/vasilis/LMTHING/lmthing/sdk/org/scenarios/06-tanzania/fixtures/tanzaniamemories.md:2:Vasilis is planning a fully booked international trip in August 2026, traveling with a companion named Athina Mari. The trip spans Cairo (Egypt), Arusha and the northern Tanzania safari circuit, Zanzibar, and Dar es Salaam, running August 3–20. The trip combines cultural sightseeing in Cairo, a group camping safari through Tarangire, Lake Manyara, and Ngorongoro Crater, beach time in Zanzibar, and city exploration in Dar es Salaam. All flights, accommodations, the safari, and key dining are confirmed and fully organized.\n/home/vasilis/LMTHING/lmthing/sdk/org/scenarios/06-tanzania/fixtures/tanzaniamemories.md:44:Tanzania e-visa is mandatory online ($50/person) at visa.immigration.go.tz; visa-on-arrival no longer available as of January 2025. Zanzibar also requires separate mandatory travel insurance from the Zanzibar Insurance Corporation.\n/home/vasilis/LMTHING/lmthing/sdk/org/scenarios/06-tanzania/fixtures/tanzaniamemories.md:61:Tanzania e-visa portal: visa.immigration.go.tz\n/home/vasilis/LMTHING/lmthing/sdk/org/scenarios/IDEAS.md:122:   from a later chat turn, with the new schema live and the `db` global rebound to include it. Tanzania\n/home/vasilis/LMTHING/lmthing/sdk/org/scenarios/06-tanzania/scenario.yaml:1:id: 06-tanzania\n/home/vasilis/L